Portfolio Website

Description
A single-page portfolio website showcasing my skills, projects, and recommendations. This website is designed to provide a clean and simple way to display my work and experience.

Features
* Responsive design for mobile devices
* Smooth scrolling navigation
* Back-to-top button
* Sections for About Me, Skills, Projects, and Recommendations

Technologies Used
* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript

Installation
1. Clone the repository to your local machine using `git clone https://github.com/smoo939/smoo939.github.io.git`
2. Open the `index.html` file in a web browser to view the website

Usage
* Navigate to different sections of the website using the navigation menu
* View projects and recommendations in their respective sections
* Use the back-to-top button to quickly return to the top of the page

Contributing
If you'd like to contribute to this project, please fork the repository and submit a pull request with your changes.

